Examples
========

This section provides a brief overview of the three different features that this version of the library provides: boxplot, critical distance and LaTeX report generation. A more detailed explanation of each feature can be found in the github repository of the library at `Tutorial <https://github.com/jMetal/SAES/tree/main/notebooks/SAES_tutorial.ipynb>`_.
